          "brief_html": "<blockquote>\n<p><strong>LEARNING OBJECTIVES</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>State Fermat's Little Theorem and Euler's Theorem.</li>\n<li>Compute Euler's totient $\\phi(n)$.</li>\n<li>Use $a^{\\phi(n)-1}$ as a modular inverse when $\\gcd(a,n)=1$.</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n"
